      <h2>About P. V. Sindhu</h2>
      <p>
        Pusarla Venkata Sindhu (born 5 July 1995) is an Indian badminton player.
        Considered one of India's most successful athletes, she has won medals
        at the Olympic Games, World Championships, and World Tour tournaments.
        She is the first Indian to become a badminton world champion.
      </p>

